{"title":"利用Hexo搭建blog","uid":"9978971f2d070c10eec917053c6beae2","slug":"安装hexo","date":"2021-06-28T15:31:36.000Z","updated":"2021-06-28T16:57:59.301Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/安装hexo.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"利用Hexo搭建blog\"><a href=\"#利用Hexo搭建blog\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"利用Hexo搭建blog\"></a>利用Hexo搭建blog</h1><h2 id=\"Hexo介绍\"><a href=\"#Hexo介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo介绍\"></a>Hexo介绍</h2><p>Hexo是一款快速、简洁且高效的博客框架，<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/\">Hexo官方网站</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Hexo搭建步骤\"><a href=\"#Hexo搭建步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo搭建步骤\"></a>Hexo搭建步骤</h2><p>1.安装Git<br>2.安装Node.js<br>3.安装Hexo</p>\n<h3 id=\"首先安装Git\"><a href=\"#首先安装Git\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"首先安装Git\"></a>首先安装Git</h3><p>macOS安装Git，<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/\">Git官方网站</a><br>首先安装<a href=\"https://brew.sh/index_zh-cn\">Howbrew</a>，由于官网命令会报错，所以选择清华源。<br>终端输入命令后，按照提示操作。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Terminal\" data-language=\"Terminal\"><code class=\"language-Terminal\">&#x2F;bin&#x2F;zsh -c &quot;$(curl -fsSL https:&#x2F;&#x2F;gitee.com&#x2F;cunkai&#x2F;HomebrewCN&#x2F;raw&#x2F;master&#x2F;Homebrew.sh)&quot;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>安装成功后，安装Git</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-homebrew\" data-language=\"homebrew\"><code class=\"language-homebrew\">brew install git<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>安装成功后创建ssh key、配置git<br>1.设置username和email（github每次commit都会记录他们）</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-git\" data-language=\"git\"><code class=\"language-git\">git config --global user.name <span class=\"token string\">\"username\"</span> //用户名\ngit config --global user.email <span class=\"token string\">\"Allen.hx.Yang@gmail.com\"</span> //邮箱<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>2.通过终端命令创建ssh key</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-git\" data-language=\"git\"><code class=\"language-git\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class=\"token string\">\"Allen.hx.Yang@gmail.com\"</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>回车后有以下输出</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-git\" data-language=\"git\"><code class=\"language-git\">Last login: Sat Jan  6 14:12:16 on ttys000\nWMBdeMacBook-Pro:~ WENBO$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class=\"token string\">\"Allen.hx.Yang@gmail.com\"</span>\nGenerating public/private rsa key pair.\nEnter file in which to save the key (/Users/mac/.ssh/id_rsa): \n/Users/mac/.ssh/id_rsa already exists.\nOverwrite (y/n)? <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>y以后，会输入一个私密id_rsa密码，最后会生成id_rsa、和id_rsa.pub文件。<br>终端查看.ssh/id_rsa.pub公共密钥</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Terminal\" data-language=\"Terminal\"><code class=\"language-Terminal\">open .ssh&#x2F;id_rsa.pub <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>复制内容到GitHub–&gt;settings–&gt;SSH and GPG keys–&gt;New SSH key<br>随便填一个title，将key复制进去点Add SSH key<br>最后链接验证</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Terminal\" data-language=\"Terminal\"><code class=\"language-Terminal\">ssh -T git@github.com <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>终端输出结果</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Terminal\" data-language=\"Terminal\"><code class=\"language-Terminal\">Last login: Sat Jan  6 14:42:55 on ttys000\nWMBdeMacBook-Pro:~ WENBO$ ssh -T git@github.com \nHi Allenio! You&#39;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.\nWMBdeMacBook-Pro:~ WENBO$  <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>说明已经链接成功</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装node-js\"><a href=\"#安装node-js\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装node.js\"></a>安装node.js</h2><p><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\">node.js官网</a>下载对应版本并安装<br>完成后终端输入</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Terminal\" data-language=\"Terminal\"><code class=\"language-Terminal\">npm -v \nnode -v<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>出现版本信息，说明安装成功</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装Hexo\"><a href=\"#安装Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Hexo\"></a>安装Hexo</h2><p>安装好git和node.js后，安装Hexo<br>输入命令</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Terminal\" data-language=\"Terminal\"><code class=\"language-Terminal\">npm install -g hexo-cli<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>完成后用hexo -v查看一下版本是否安装完毕<br>接下来初始化hexo</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-terminal\" data-language=\"terminal\"><code class=\"language-terminal\">hexo init MyBlog<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>之后</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Terminal\" data-language=\"Terminal\"><code class=\"language-Terminal\">cd &#x2F;~MyBlog\nnpm install<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>新建完成后就可以配置Hexo了</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-hexo\" data-language=\"hexo\"><code class=\"language-hexo\">hexo clean\nhexo g\nhexo d<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>","feature":true,"text":"利用Hexo搭建blogHexo介绍Hexo是一款快速、简洁且高效的博客框架，Hexo官方网站 Hexo搭建步骤1.安装Git2.安装Node.js3.安装Hexo 首先安装GitmacOS安装Git，Git官方网站首先安装Howbrew，由于官网命令会报错，所以选择清华源。终端...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"配置环境","slug":"配置环境","count":1,"path":"api/categories/配置环境.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E